&\qquad+ (968 - 272)(967 - 273)(966 - 274) - (999 - 222)^3
\end{align*}

output:
**Step 1: Calculate each subtraction.**

-  \begin{align*} 972 - 268 = 693 \end{align*}
-  \begin{align*} 973 - 267 = 693 \end{align*}
-  \begin{align*} 974 - 266 = 691 \end{align*}
